    <picture><source media="(max-width: 1311px)" srcset="https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-375.b54dfd261242.jpg 375w,https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-720.7e78f84a25ad.jpg 720w,https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-976.430dd72bf6ff.jpg 976w,https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-1232.b51ad1fd7e76.jpg 1232w,https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-1450.ccdd4743516e.jpg 1450w" sizes="(min-width: 768px) calc((100vw - 32px) / 2),calc(100vw - 32px)" width="1450" height="723"><source srcset="https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-desktop-344.7eaf508dbf4c.jpg 344w,https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-desktop-664.be5a1d87c1f7.jpg 664w" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) 332px,calc((100vw - 64px) / 4)" width="664" height="664"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/home/2024/ai-gallery/builders-mobile-720.7e78f84a25ad.jpg" alt="Builders"></picture>
  </div>
  
  
    <div class="m24-c-gallery-tile-tag">
      
      프로그램
    </div>
  
  <div class="m24-c-gallery-tile-content">
    
      <p class="m24-c-gallery-tile-desc">Mozilla Builders는 맞춤형 협업과 프로그래밍, 커뮤니티를 통해 독립 개발자가 혁신적인 오픈 소스 AI 프로젝트를 만들 수 있도록 돕습니다.</p>
    
    
      <p class="m24-c-gallery-tile-cta">
        <span>더 보기</span>
      </p>
    
    </div>
</div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
  



